content.rendered:
Directed by Santhossh Jagarlapudi

Written by Santhossh Jagarlapudi. Srujanamani

Star Jagapathi Babu (Parthasaradhi). Sachin Khedekar. Shanu Kumar (Babu). Ravi Prakash. Satya. Ketika Sharma (Rithika). Naga Shaurya (Pardhu)

Language Telugu

Producers Sharat Marar. Narayan Das Narang. Puskur Ram Mohan Rao

Production Northstar Entertainment .Sree Venkateswara Cinemas
